---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import rominaWilmot from '../assets/about-bg-romina-wilmot.webp';
---
<header class="relative lg:pt-32 lg:pb-20 pt-40 pb-28 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-16">
    <div class="flex-1 z-10">
      
      <h1 class="font-headline text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-primary leading-[1.1] tracking-tight mb-8">
        Meet <br/>
        <span class="text-secondary italic">Romina Wilmot</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-lg">
        My clients can leverage my unique background and strong connections.  With over 20 years of professional experience, I've helped mid to large size healthcare organizations grow.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex-1 relative">
      <div class="relative mt-16 z-10 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl transform md:translate-x-4">
        <Image alt="Romina Wilmot" class="w-full aspect-[4/5] object-cover" src={rominaWilmot} />
      </div>
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-secondary/20 rounded-2xl -translate-x-8 translate-y-8 z-0"></div>
      <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 bg-white/90 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-xl z-20 max-w-[280px] border border-slate-100">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary mb-2" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">format_quote</span>
        <p class="text-sm font-body italic text-slate-600 leading-snug">"If your healthcare or human service organization is looking to engage with both the community and healthcare providers, I've walked the walk."</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>